<H1 align=center>GUIDING PRINCIPLES<H1>
<font size=6 color=darkgreen>
<p>
The mission statement supports this vision while also conveying how they plan to realize it:

They nurture the global students into men and women, who will be leaders of distinction, committed to spirit of excellence, through high quality 
education imparted by globally experienced and caring teachers building strong virtues and values while focusing on all round development, creativity 
and entrepreneurship.
<p>
<H4 ailign=left>CORE VALUES<H4>
To that end, several core values infuse everything they do at GIIS:
<ul>
<li>Manage with information and metrics
<li>Agility and Adaptability
<li>Honesty, Integrity and Ethical Practices
<li>Attitude before Knowledge
<li>Teamwork
<li>Mentor, Coach and Make a Difference
<li>Ambience for Learning
</ul>
